{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/00.gif?t=1707581776\" /><br>The story begins with a massive fire that destroyed an ongoing ritual,<br> causing ghosts and ghouls to run rampant in both the celestial and mortal realms.<br><br>To restart the ritual, the protagonist &quot;Hong-Niang&quot; must assist her parents in purchasing the ingredients required for the ceremony in town.<br>And with the assistance of two mythical creatures, &quot;Taotie&quot; and &quot;Fu-Xi,&quot; complete the mission; <br>thwart the mischief-makers disrupting the ceremony, restoring order to both the celestial and mortal realms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><i></i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/01.gif?t=1707581776\" /><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Chinese-style art and architectural scenes.</li></ul></strong>Whether it's the magnificent Jiu Ge Restaurant or the uniquely themed town, every map is worth exploring and savoring.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/02_en.gif?t=1707581776\" /><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shadow puppetry stories and real recipes.</li></ul></strong>Legendary stories presented through paper-cut shadow puppetry and actual mooncake recipes used in the game provide you with a deeper sense of immersion and surprises!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/03.gif?t=1707581776\" /><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Two battle modes and four difficulty levels to choose from.</li></ul></strong>Different choices will affect the gameplay; we offer three difficulty levels and a non-combat version for you to choose freely.<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Parodying mythical stories.</li></ul></strong>A funny and entertaining plot that breaks the established impression of mythical stories! Suitable for players who enjoy lighthearted and cheerful narratives.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Follow Us</h2><i></i><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/ICON_Twitter.jpg?t=1707581776\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/blank.png?t=1707581776\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/ICON_FaceBook.jpg?t=1707581776\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/blank.png?t=1707581776\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/ICON_YouTube.jpg?t=1707581776\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/extras/blank.png?t=1707581776\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Special Thanks</h2>Assistance with publishing the game on Steam: <br><br>Maker\u88fd\u9020\u6a5f- Chimaki\u3000<br><br>Multi-language system plugins:<br>Mirai\u3000<br><br>Promotional video BGM:<br>\u9b54\u738b\u9b42\u3000","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2567250?t=1707581776","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2567250?t=1707581776","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1707581776","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1707581776","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567250/ex